-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    SopStream - A helper utility for controlling SopCast
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

----- Summary

This application provides a command line interface to the sp-sc SopCast tool
for Linux.

It allows the user to download a SopCast channel list and select a channel to
start streaming by name, rather than channel number.

-----

----- Dependencies

This utility requires the following:

    sp-sc
    Command line Linux version of SopCast.
    http://sopcast-player.googlecode.com/files/sp-auth-3.2.6.tar.gz

    libstdc++5
    The GNU Standard C++ Library v3

-----